p.k: Sexy Nina Milano answers an online ad to buy a used laptop, much to her husband s delight. When Keiran Lee shows up at her home with the laptop, Nina leads him to the bedroom and seduces him into trading it for sex instead. Keiran is hesitant, but can't resist the sexy trade offer. Little does he know, Nina's husband is perfectly aware of what s going on and watches through a peephole in the next room.
